<section id="projects" class="projects">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="section-title">研究项目</h2>
    <div class="projects-grid">
      <article class="project-card">
        <div class="project-header">
          <div class="project-category">IEEE SMC 2025 (CCF-C)</div>
          <h3 class="project-title">DPGNet: Dual Prior Guided Network for Surgical Instrument Segmentation</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="project-content">
           <p class="project-description">
             提出了一种双先验引导网络用于外科器械分割，创新性地结合了CNN与ViT架构的优势。
             通过设计的Mamba增强适配器和多上下文引导解码器，有效利用了视觉基础模型(VFM)的先验知识，显著提升了分割精度。
           </p>
          <div class="project-tags">
            <span class="tag">CNN</span>
            <span class="tag">ViT</span>
            <span class="tag">Mamba</span>
            <span class="tag">SAM2</span>
            <span class="tag">VFM</span>
          </div>
          <div class="project-achievement">
            <span class="achievement-label">成果</span>
            <span class="achievement-text">
              在 Kvasir-Instrument 和 EndoVis2017 数据集上，mIoU分别提升4.2%和8.3%，达到SOTA性能
            </span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="project-card">
        <div class="project-header">
          <div class="project-category">CVIU (CCF-B)</div>
          <h3 class="project-title">DGMCN: Depth-Guided Multi-modal Collaboration Network for Robust Polyp Segmentation in Endoscopic Images</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="project-content">
           <p class="project-description">
             开发了深度引导的多模态协作网络，用于内窥镜图像中的鲁棒息肉分割。
             基于UNet架构进行改进，设计了DGMCN和DAMUNet模块来增强多模态特征提取和协作能力。
           </p>
          <div class="project-tags">
            <span class="tag">UNet</span>
            <span class="tag">Multi-modal</span>
            <span class="tag">Polyp Segmentation</span>
            <span class="tag">Endoscopic Images</span>
          </div>
          <div class="project-achievement">
            <span class="achievement-label">成果</span>
            <span class="achievement-text">
              在 Kvasir-SEG 数据集上，mIoU提升8.5%，Dice提升6.7%
            </span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .projects {
    padding: 6rem 2rem;
    background: #f8fafc;
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .section-title {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    color: #1a1a2e;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .projects-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(500px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .project-card {
    background: white;
    border-radius: 16px;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 6px -1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    transition: transform 0.3s, box-shadow 0.3s;
  }

  .project-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    box-shadow: 0 20px 25px -5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
  }

  .project-header {
    padding: 2rem 2rem 1rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
    color: white;
  }

  .project-category {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    opacity: 0.9;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .project-title {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    line-height: 1.4;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .project-content {
    padding: 1.5rem 2rem 2rem;
  }

  .project-description {
    color: #4a4a4a;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .project-tags {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .tag {
    padding: 0.375rem 0.75rem;
    background: #e0e7ff;
    color: #4338ca;
    border-radius: 20px;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .project-achievement {
    padding: 1rem;
    background: #fef3c7;
    border-radius: 8px;
    border-left: 4px solid #f59e0b;
  }

  .achievement-label {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #d97706;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }

  .achievement-text {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: #92400e;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .projects-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
